
                                      ; Tic Tac toe
                                      ; Guy Fedorkow
                                      ; Sep 26, 2024

                                      ; May 24, 2026 - there's a non-critical bug still in the display of the WW
                                      ; move in FF3 -- the first move is computed by table, and the result is the cell number
                                      ; multiplied by 3.  To display the move properly, I "should" divide the number by 3.

                                      ; Simple game of tic-tac-toe written in Whirlwind assembly code.
                                      ; The game displays on the WW CRT, and can be played with the light gun
                                      ; (As of Sep 26, it's a two-person game, i.e., i alternates X and O plays)

                                      ; Geometry
                                      ; the basic game board is laid out on a 16x16 grid as follows:

                                      ;  cell 0   | cell 1   |  cell 2
                                      ;  @(4,12)  | @(8,12)  |  @(12,12)
                                      ; --------------------------------
                                      ;  cell 3   | cell 4   |  cell 5
                                      ;  @(4,8)   | @(8,8)   |  @(12,8)
                                      ; --------------------------------
                                      ;  cell 6   | cell 7   |  cell 8
                                      ;  @(4,4)   | @(8,4)   |  @(12,4)

                                      ;----------- old layout ----------
                                      ;  cell 6   | cell 7   |  cell 8
                                      ;  @(4,12)  | @(8,12)  |  @(12,12)
                                      ; --------------------------------
                                      ;  cell 3   | cell 4   |  cell 5
                                      ;  @(4,8)   | @(8,8)   |  @(12,8)
                                      ; --------------------------------
                                      ;  cell 0   | cell 1   |  cell 2
                                      ;  @(4,4)   | @(8,4)   |  @(12,4)
                                      ;-------------------------------

                                      .org 0
                                zero:
@0000:000000                 const_0: .word 0                  ; @@WrittenBy apc_table_ts igb_table_ts gl_ca_addr ReadBy a0054 ca_addr a0173 dd_y_arg dd_x_arg dc_y_arg dc_x_arg dn_y_arg dn_x1_arg dw_y_arg dw_x_arg dt_y_arg dt_x_arg lgh_x1_arg lgh_y1_arg apc_ca0 a0610 a0631 a0667 a0720 a0725 a0743 a0761 a0766 char_conv2 a1014 a1021 a1040 a1100 CWLD a1124 a1132 a1146 a1155 a1167 a1177 a1204 a1211 a1216 a1223 a1230 a1235 a1242 a1262 a1300 a1306 a1323 a1343 a1350 a1371 a1375 a1401 PRaddr PRLOOP a1503 char_conv1 a2453 a2457 a2660 a2672 a2715 a2720 JumpedToBy gb_state_sp a0176 a0345 a0362 a0404 a0425 a0447 a0466 a0505 a0515 light_gun_cell_hit_ret a0566 a0574 a0600 a0601 a0603 a0637 rgs_ret GMRET MHRET CWRET CMRET TMRET TFRET PBRET PSRET PBNRET PPRET PRRET PCMRET PHWRET PCWRET PDRET PBMRET PSTRET a2465 a2724
